{
  "texts": [
    "In the field of Orthopedic Surgery, machine learning has already enabled detection of fractures, loose implants, or even helped diagnose tumors [10].",
    "Limitations of ChatGPTChatGPT represents a milestone in ML in that it builds on previous GPT 3.5 models with the addition of a reinforcement learning technique so that users can continuously offer feedback to shape its behavior [1,3].",
    "However despite this, it has important restrictions worth considering.",
    "Its training on GPT 3.5 is limited in scope until the end of 2021, with it having inadequate knowledge of events beyond that time frame [1].",
    "This has often led to it having a tendency to fabricate references or have incorrect reasoning when solving problems that require logic beyond this date [1,[12][13][14]."
  ]
}